{"tid":1097007,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"不滿中國觀眾比賽時狂報位 CSGO選手怒比中指以示抗議","createTime":"2019-04-08T06:09:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-08T07:32:39.000Z","uid":185134,"like":43,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"039e42828a100274624d3bd052efc1b433a3800c","tid":1097007,"uid":185134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-08T06:09:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://pgw.udn.com.tw/gw/photo.php?u=https://uc.udn.com.tw/photo/2019/04/08/99/6148106.png&amp;x=0&amp;y=0&amp;sw=0&amp;sh=0&amp;sl=W&amp;fw=1050\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpgw.udn.com.tw%2Fgw%2Fphoto.php%3Fu%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fuc.udn.com.tw%2Fphoto%2F2019%2F04%2F08%2F99%2F6148106.png%26x%3D0%26y%3D0%26sw%3D0%26sh%3D0%26sl%3DW%26fw%3D1050&h=2b4bd9e7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n射擊遊戲選擇藏匿位置埋伏敵人也是戰術執行的重要環節，但卻被觀眾嚴重影響！日前中國上海舉辦的《CS：GO》SLi第七賽季（StarSeries &amp; i-League CS:GO Season 7）聯賽中，Renegades戰隊的澳洲選手Gratisfaction不滿台下的中國觀眾將他的位置暴露給敵隊知道，直接怒對觀眾比中指。<br />\n<br />\n當時Gratisfaction在俗稱「三明治」的區域埋伏著，而台下觀眾則用英文喊「Sandwich」，聲音非常清晰到連官方頻道的直播影片也聽得一清二楚。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://clips.twitch.tv/HungryMildSandstormNononoCat\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fclips.twitch.tv%2FHungryMildSandstormNononoCat&d=vUt%2FZqt5lAJzOS14TgBfp1c%2F7AvELiRjmt2A4bWGPaQ%3D&h=f15766ca\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://clips.twitch.tv/HungryMildSandstormNononoCat</a><br />\n<br />\n賽後Gratisfaction選手發布一則推特，表示他比中指的行為並不是針對敵方隊伍，而是比給那些「報位」的觀眾看的。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://pgw.udn.com.tw/gw/photo.php?u=https://uc.udn.com.tw/photo/2019/04/08/99/6148214.png&amp;x=0&amp;y=0&amp;sw=0&amp;sh=0&amp;sl=W&amp;fw=1050\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpgw.udn.com.tw%2Fgw%2Fphoto.php%3Fu%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fuc.udn.com.tw%2Fphoto%2F2019%2F04%2F08%2F99%2F6148214.png%26x%3D0%26y%3D0%26sw%3D0%26sh%3D0%26sl%3DW%26fw%3D1050&h=fa54eb50&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n而中國網友對於Gratisfaction選手比出中指的行為相當生氣，揚言欲抵制Gratisfaction參加比賽。面對中國網友大量的質疑聲浪，Gratisfaction後續又在推特發表道歉聲明，說明「很抱歉我的行為讓你們感覺被冒犯，但我仍是非常喜愛中國粉絲的！」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://pgw.udn.com.tw/gw/photo.php?u=https://uc.udn.com.tw/photo/2019/04/08/99/6148266.png&amp;x=0&amp;y=0&amp;sw=0&amp;sh=0&amp;sl=W&amp;fw=1050\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpgw.udn.com.tw%2Fgw%2Fphoto.php%3Fu%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fuc.udn.com.tw%2Fphoto%2F2019%2F04%2F08%2F99%2F6148266.png%26x%3D0%26y%3D0%26sw%3D0%26sh%3D0%26sl%3DW%26fw%3D1050&h=9d7b0f55&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n即使Gratisfaction直接對觀眾比中指並非十分恰當，但也有網友反應當時人在現場，觀眾報位的聲音連坐在第一排都聽得非常清楚，質疑主辦方的隔音設備是否需要加強。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://game.udn.com/game/story/10445/3742830\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgame.udn.com%2Fgame%2Fstory%2F10445%2F3742830&d=vUt%2FZqt5lAJzOS14TgBfp1c%2F7AvELiRjmt2A4bWGPaQ%3D&h=72a84419\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://game.udn.com/game/story/10445/3742830</a>"},{"pid":"1b1fa08682b773e1a4fb5d5a0a53b394d19dce37","tid":1097007,"uid":168366,"like":40,"dislike":0,"score":40,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-08T06:11:28.000Z","msg":"支那人最叻就係出術<br />\n全世界都對支那人太仁慈"},{"pid":"b3abbde820dce52da2063c76ce44c8e020acad83","tid":1097007,"uid":229609,"like":61,"dislike":0,"score":61,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-08T06:12:20.000Z","msg":"明明係大陸賤種唔啱,點解要道歉?"},{"pid":"ce3dd446f8e7b80ae996149be24165f247c68e83","tid":1097007,"uid":46370,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"quote":{"pid":"b3abbde820dce52da2063c76ce44c8e020acad83","tid":1097007,"uid":229609,"like":61,"dislike":0,"score":61,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-08T06:12:20.000Z","msg":"明明係大陸賤種唔啱,點解要道歉?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-08T06:13:58.000Z","msg":"這就是中國"},{"pid":"8ac8bfcd212eedb4c189ad62fc4d215f02cb5712","tid":1097007,"uid":10757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-08T06:15:00.000Z","msg":"同韓狗一撚樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f53c2e2a7fb13addf43c914ac65f64fd19d98f2","tid":1097007,"uid":95,"like":4,"dislike":0,"s